<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Toque Mágico</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;
}

body{
    background:linear-gradient(180deg,#ffffff,#ffe4ef);
    min-height:100vh;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    overflow:hidden;
    position:relative;
}

/* Flores */
.flower{
    position:absolute;
    font-size:40px;
    opacity:.18;
    animation:float 8s ease-in-out infinite;
}

.f1{top:5%;left:5%;}
.f2{top:12%;right:8%;}
.f3{bottom:10%;left:10%;}
.f4{bottom:8%;right:8%;}
.f5{top:45%;left:3%;}
.f6{top:45%;right:3%;}

@keyframes float{
    0%,100%{transform:translateY(0);}
    50%{transform:translateY(-18px);}
}

.card{
    width:90%;
    max-width:500px;
    background:#fff;
    border-radius:25px;
    padding:40px;
    text-align:center;
    box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(255,105,180,.25);
    border:3px solid #ffc0cb;
}

.logo{
    font-size:55px;
}

h1{
    color:#e91e63;
    margin-top:10px;
    margin-bottom:10px;
}

p{
    color:#666;
    margin-bottom:30px;
}

.btn{
    display:block;
    width:100%;
    text-decoration:none;
    padding:16px;
    margin:15px 0;
    border-radius:50px;
    color:white;
    font-size:18px;
    font-weight:600;
    transition:.3s;
}

.whatsapp{
    background:#25D366;
}

.whatsapp:hover{
    transform:scale(1.03);
}

.instagram{
    background:linear-gradient(45deg,#833AB4,#E1306C,#F77737);
}

.instagram:hover{
    transform:scale(1.03);
}

footer{
    margin-top:25px;
    color:#e91e63;
    font-size:14px;
}
</style>

</head>
<body>

<div class="flower f1">🌸</div>
<div class="flower f2">🌷</div>
<div class="flower f3">🌺</div>
<div class="flower f4">🌼</div>
<div class="flower f5">🌹</div>
<div class="flower f6">💐</div>

<div class="card">

<div class="logo">🌸</div>

<h1>Toque Mágico</h1>

<p>
Delicadeza, charme e beleza em cada detalhe. 💕
</p>

<a class="btn whatsapp"
href="https://wa.me/5511943374143"
target="_blank">
📱 Entre em contato pelo WhatsApp
</a>

<a class="btn instagram"
href="https://www.instagram.com/toque.magicolingerie?igsh=MXNsdWhodGk5dWd6ZQ=="
target="_blank">
📷 Visite nosso Instagram
</a>

<footer>
🌸 Toque Mágico © 2026 🌸
</footer>

</div>

</body>
</html>
